Player equips item 

Prerequisite: Player has Displayed Inventory
Player can view items to equip from inventory
Play can preview item to equip from inventory, and a brief description of what each item does 
Player can exit preview OR 
    Player can equip item by choosing in preview screen
Player can choose item to equip item from main inventory page
Player can unequip item from main inventory page
     If item not equipped, return error, “item needs to be equipped” 
Player can have only one item 
    If more than one item equipped, return error “Cannot choose more than one item” 

Player confirms item choice 
   If player does not confirm item choice, return error “Please confirm item choice” 

Player returns to main screen(?) After confirming 
